## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Recording captures all interaction types with correct context
- [ ] Replay shows frames in sequence with accurate timing
- [ ] Step forward/backward works correctly
- [ ] Frame inspector shows full context at each point
- [ ] Errors highlighted prominently in timeline
- [ ] Annotations persist and display correctly
- [ ] Search finds frames by content
- [ ] Export produces valid, importable files
- [ ] Shareable links work for team debugging

## Technical Considerations

- Storage optimization: compress frame content (Brotli)
- Large sessions: lazy load frames, paginate API
- Privacy: option to redact sensitive content before sharing
- Retention policy: auto-delete replays after N days
- Performance: recording should add < 5% overhead

